  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p></p><p>To assist the Project Manager or Project Engineer in the daily execution of work.</p><p>To supervise the work of sub-contractors and in-house workers.</p><p>To work closely with other site operations staff to meet the project schedule.</p><p>Ensure installation is carried out as per construction drawings.</p><p>To monitor the progress and quality of work being performed by workers.</p><p>Ensure that works are executed within an acceptable standard of workmanship.</p><p>Plan, schedule, and coordinate polymer application projects, ensuring timely delivery and adherence to specifications.</p><p>Attend the daily tool-box meeting and convey clear instruction accordingly.</p><p>Implement safety procedures, ensure regulatory compliance, and manage incident responses.</p><p>Update clients on progress, address concerns, and maintain project documentation.</p><p>Understand and ensure compliance in project requirement and scope of work.</p>",
